summary:
Found this little dude in the woods fishing for minnows. I knelt down and he whispered into my ear, 
"There are different levels...
body:
Found this little dude in the woods fishing for minnows. I knelt down and he whispered into my ear,

“There are different levels of intersex and assigning biological sex is more complicated than people think, gender is a social construct and no one else’s business other than oneself”.

Then got up and left.
